column4: Hey all, what's a good repo to add to get a bunch of extra packages? I'm trying to install zabbix on ubuntu-server, and it wants libsnmp5
would linsnmp9 be fine if I just ignore the "unmet dependency"?
apt-cache search libsnmp - see which versions you have available.....
it's generally safe to use things with higher version numbers thatn asked for, isn't it? I know it isn't always, but as a rule
